{"tid":1183644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白田邨60歲男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-06-03T05:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T05:47:37.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c05765267bf4023a8f42a3ada41293be76b82915","tid":1183644,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ekvrmvf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEkvrmvf.png&h=d81e1322&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/r1GJ8ag.png[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1GJ8ag.png%5B%2Fimg&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=9ab251e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/r1GJ8ag.png[/img</a><br />\n警方在現場調查。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n石硤尾白田邨昌田樓，中午12時，一名年約60歲的男子由高處墮下，跌在出入口外空地。救援人員到場經檢驗，證實該男子已告不治。警方正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=f1c851c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"93f2eb0195dd6b69000bab5d872b9c27ef9da500","tid":1183644,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHr6mvs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHr6mvs.png&h=8199771c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea42f034c21676cbe359e1d6e2102314c379978c","tid":1183644,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a109011ebe888bb29b126ca6dab9cdeef2bee152","tid":1183644,"uid":29080,"like